			Gearheart is an especially tough level 12 warrior<BR>
type NPC.  When you kill him you get a box.  You<BR>
give that box to the warrior guild guy (far right)<BR>
and he gives you some xp, a faction adjustment,<BR>
and an item worth between 5-10 gp at a shop.<BR>
A very worthwhile quest if you can kill him ;).<BR>

