			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Gearheart is exactly level 26.  No more, no less.  I hunted faeries between 24-28 and I watched as the con message changed with level.  At 26, he conned white to me every time he spawned.  He is obviously tougher than 26, he hits very hard.  If you're a druid, you can harmony him (if successful with unlink the faeries from him) then snare, run, nuke, run, nuke, run, etc.  With my wisdom at 163, I barely had enough mana to solo him at 25-26.  Not to mention the fact that harmony doesn't always work and you have to then snare a few faerie guards that are also chasing you.  Luckily the Mistmoore zone is just a short run to the south.
			</font>
	
